{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-tsx","path":"/tech/2020/03/11/apt添加代理.html","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"id":"04f822ce-866e-5f37-806a-eba771478aca","excerpt":"为 apt 添加代理 我的上帝啊，这两天都在忙活代理（翻译腔）。 系统全局下的http_proxy似乎对 apt 无效，需要单独设置。 增加代理","html":"<h1>为 apt 添加代理</h1>\n<p>我的上帝啊，这两天都在忙活代理（翻译腔）。</p>\n<p>系统全局下的<code>http_proxy</code>似乎对 apt 无效，需要单独设置。</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-shell\">sudo nano /etc/apt/apt.conf.d/proxy.conf\n</code></pre>\n<p>增加代理</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-shell\">Acquire {\n  HTTP::proxy \"http://127.0.0.1:8080\";\n  HTTPS::proxy \"http://127.0.0.1:8080\";\n}\n</code></pre>","frontmatter":{"category":"tech"},"fields":{"slug":"/tech/2020/03/11/apt添加代理.html","date":"March 11, 2020","title":"apt添加代理"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/tech/2020/03/11/apt添加代理.html","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/tech/2020/03/11/snap添加代理.html","title":"snap添加代理"},"frontmatter":{"category":"tech"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/tech/2020/03/15/Coding.net使用Jenkins实现自动部署CI&CD.html","title":"Coding.net使用Jenkins实现自动部署CI&CD"},"frontmatter":{"category":"tech"}}}}}